<WorkLayout title='Swiset - Study Case'>
  <main>
    <img src='/images/marco/marco.webp' alt='' />
    <p class='uppercase text-xl text-[#667085] font-bold my-6'>
      published on <span class='font-normal'>12 SEP 2022</span>
    </p>
    <h1 class='text-4xl'>Marco, Mobile Application - UX/UI Case Study.</h1>
    <img src='/images/marco/marco-tags.webp' alt='' class='my-6' />
    <Paragraph title='About'>
      Marco is an app that helps people to know what is happening in their city
      with a lot of events and activities to do, Marco facilitates contact with
      the creators of events and those interested, is an excellent tool for both
      people who want to go out and learn more about their city and for all
      tourists who want to know the city they visit.
    </Paragraph>

    <div class='flex gap-4 my-8 flex-wrap justify-center'>
      <Tag text='👨‍💻 My Role: UI/UX Design' />
      <Tag text='🎨 Tools: Figma' />
      <Tag text='⌛ Duration: 3 Weeks' />
      <Tag text='🙋 Audience:  16 - 50 years old' />
    </div>
  </main>
